OL,3,CMan who died in house fire named
OL,4,Clocally
OL,6,FA 45-year-old man who died in a major
OL,7,Ffire in Cumbria has been named locally
OL,8,Fas Ben Taylor.
OL,10,FMr. Taylor died inside a property -
OL,11,Fwhere the fire is believed to have
OL,12,Fstarted - on Main Street in Kirkby
OL,13,FLonsdale last weekend. He was
OL,14,Fpronounced dead at the scene after his
OL,15,Fbody was recovered from the fire just
OL,16,Fafter 6:30am on 8 December 2024.
OL,18,FOne woman from the town said: "It's
OL,19,Fvery sad. The family is a big part of
OL,20,Fthis community, and my thoughts are
OL,21,Fwith them."
