OL,6,FA local couple said: "He was very
OL,7,Fhelpful, he was a wonderful person and
OL,8,Fwe're very sorry that he's died."
OL,10,FA man also said: "They're a big family
OL,11,Fin the town, all my thoughts to his
OL,12,Ffamily, it's obviously a very
OL,13,Fdifficult time."
OL,15,FThe local community at the time were
OL,16,Ftold to keep doors and windows closed
OL,17,Fwhilst Cumbria Police and other
OL,18,Femergency services dealt with the
OL,19,Fincident.
