OL,6,FThe town's Christmas market, which was
OL,7,Fdue to take place on Sunday, was also
OL,8,Fcancelled.
OL,10,FA GoFundMe page organised by Kirkby
OL,11,FLonsdale Rugby Union Football Club has
OL,12,Falso raised more than #13,000 to
OL,13,Fsupport Jakob, a player for the club,
OL,14,Fwho has lost his Cumbrian home from
OL,15,Fthe major fire on 8 December 2024.
