OL,3,CMan who died in house fire named
OL,4,Clocally
OL,6,FJakob, from New Zealand, has lost
OL,7,F"every possession". Brian Gregory,
OL,8,Forganiser of the fundraiser and
OL,9,Fchairman of the rugby club, said: "He
OL,10,Fnow needs our community to support
OL,11,Fhim. Even a few pounds can help him
OL,12,Fstart to rebuild his life, and show
OL,13,Fthat in Kirkby Lonsdale and in the
OL,14,Fwider rugby community no one stands
OL,15,Falone.
OL,17,F"Thank you for bringing some hope and
OL,18,Fcomfort to a grieving community."
